Base Drush Make files to use as base for build a Drupal distribution or a development sandbox.
Contains a selection of commonly used modules, selected by my interests on site building.
For use just type:
$drush make file.make [install_directory]

Some modules/themes/libraries have a fixed version defined for make sure of compatibility,
Always check the files to see if the specified versions suit to your case.

Contains:
- drupal-install-6.x.make (outdated)
- drupal-baseinstall-7.x.make
- drupal-simple-7.x.make

